snippet.title: TY the Tasmanian Tiger HD on Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
TY the Tasmanian Tiger is back like a boomerang on the Nintendo Switch. Now you can save the world from Boss Cass on the go and in HD!

Thanks to our mates (https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/2031740950/ty-console), the game is now available digitally on Nintendo eShop. 

In 2021, there were also Nintendo Switch physical releases. There's TY1, and also a special bundle edition with TY2 as a digital download + boomberang USB with digital goodies. See https://www.kromestudios.com/ty/ for more informationl

Cheers!
